summary: Adds the Void Elf race. Its just a copy of high elves with different skin colors and abilities.
descriptionHtml:
skills are as follows...

One handed +10
Light Armor+5
Sneak+5
Destruction+15
Conjuration+15

Ability...

Void Blood: gives 50 extra health and magikca.


Bugs: for some reason this mod adds argonian hair styles to this race and high elves when creating a character. If any one know how to fix this any help would be welcomed.
EDIT: turns out another mod i was using was doing this:)


This should be compatible with everything because it only uses vanilla assets
(i do use cbbe and apachii sky hair too)
___________________________________________________________________________________

V. 2 added racial power

Void\'s Hold.. Gives +100 Magicka for 120 seconds

and now comes packaged with RaceCompatibility.esm
